":19.626512,"lng":-155.986455,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Whole-person healing with acupuncture, functional medicine & soul care. Community clinic & wellness center in Kailua-Kona. Insurance accepted.","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"28485e6d-7f46-46e8-9a20-a1454d170160","name":"Kona Health & Aesthetics","image":"http://static1.squarespace.com/static/6413a2c7c4366d2cbcfeaa55/t/6729269747aa8967313c47da/1730750107908/ADVANCED+IV+Center.png?format=1500w","modality":"Alternative Therapy, Naturopathic, IV Therapy","modalities":["Alternative Therapy","Naturopathic","IV Therapy"],"location":"Kailua-Kona","rating":5,"lat":19.640423,"lng":-155.990412,"services":[],"tier":"free","description":"Located on the Big Island, Kona Health & Aesthetics is Hawaii’s most progressive, integrative medical center. The experienced team, under the medical direction of the practice’s founder Dr. Kristina Roberts, includes a mix of medical professionals who specialize in both traditional and alternative therapies, including naturopathic and holistic medicine. The dedicated team focuses on healing the body by identifying the root cause of illness, instead of focusing on the disease or symptoms.\n\nIn addition to managing your primary medical needs, the team at Kona Health & Aesthetics specializes in intravenous therapy, peptide therapy, and weight loss protocols. To improve your overall health and well-being, patients also have access to nutrition guidance and hormone therapy. ","centerType":"wellness_center","centerTypeLabel":"Wellness Center","island":"big_island","updatedAt":"2026-04-02T09:31:30.328449+00:00","photos":[],"workingHours":{},"acceptsNewClients":true,"verified":true},{"id":"d9dd5eea-0088-4e3e-a657-bc69e9c0b93c","name":"Radiant Wellness","image":"https://radiantwellnesshi.com/wp-conte